      Hotel details
      On Kololo Game Reserve, this quaint lodge is surrounded by African bush, and borders Welgevonden Game Reserve. It's 29 km from Marakele National Park and 38.2 km from the town centre. … MORE

      The relaxed cottages feature wood beams, stone walls and sitting areas. Most have thatched roofs and include free Wi-Fi. Some have outdoor terraces with kitchenettes, while others have indoor kitchens, and living rooms with fireplaces and/or TVs.

      Free game drives, guided walks and safari-based kids' activities are available. The main lodge houses a laid-back restaurant offering panoramic bush views. Other amenities include an outdoor pool and an event hall.
